headline: Xcel Energy Chief Operations Officer to Retire This Summer
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 03, 2025--Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) announced today that Timothy O’Connor, executive vice president, chief operations officer, will retire from the company this summer after nearly two decades of service.
